It's hard to be hopeful when you're working hard but struggling with rising costs. But this isn't inevitable. Decisions made in Ottawa have put profits for big business before the needs of people. We'll make different choices & this is how we get there:https://www.ndp.ca/commitments

Depuis trop longtemps, les gouvernements à Ottawa priorisent les profits des ultra-riches et des grandes entreprises aux dépends des besoins de la population. Les choses doivent changer. Nous ferons des choix différents pour de meilleurs résultats :https://www.npd.ca/vision

Too many Canadians are losing hope in a future that seems determined to count them out. It doesn't have to be this way. Today we're sharing our commitments to you – a vision of a more prosperous & fairer Canada for all of us. Our New Deal for People: https://www.ndp.ca/commitments pic.twitter.com/JSf6vmZz9C

De plus en plus de gens perdent espoir en l'avenir et se sentent abandonnés. On ne peut pas continuer dans cette voie. Aujourd'hui, nous présentons notre vision pour un pays plus prospère, durable et équitable. Voici nos engagements envers vous : https://www.npd.ca/vision pic.twitter.com/1ZtZfzQtyx

Unlike Justin Trudeau’s Carbon Tax that does nothing to reduce emissions, my plan - A Real Plan to Protect Our Environment - will take meaningful action to protect our environment while leaving money in Canadians pockets.pic.twitter.com/5N0ZHU9Ta7
